User
  - (ID) User ID
  - (String) Facebook ID
  - (String) Twitter ID
  - (String) Google ID
  - (String) Name
  - (String) Email
  - (String) IP
  - (Enum String) Status
    * blocked
    * normal

Tale
  - (ID) Tale ID
  - (String) Title
  - (String) Author
  - (Date) Publication
  - (String) Content
  - (Array Tag ID) Tags

Tags_Definintions
  - (ID) Tag ID
  - (String) Name
  - (String) Description

Tags
  - (ID) Tale ID
  - (ID) Tag ID

History
  - (ID) User ID
  - (ID) Tale ID
  - (Boolean) liked

Analysis
  - (ID) Analysis ID
  - (ID) Tale ID
  - (ID) User ID
  - (String) Content

Messages
  - (ID) Message ID
  - (ID) User ID
  - (ID) source
  - (String) Content

Illustrations
  - (ID) Illustration ID
  - (ID) User ID
  - (ID) source

Topics
  - (ID) User ID
  - (String) Content

